   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>N.N. to Pnepheros, greeting. We have taken you to Kerkeosiris and Areos kome on the 27th in order that you may gather your vineyards pending the settlement in regard to them. The 32nd year, Phaophi 27.</ab>
